injury.description: Aug 27: Lloyd (hamstring) is on Green Bay's initial 53-man roster, while fellow running back AJ Dillon (neck) has been placed on season-ending injured reserve, Matt Schneidman of The Athletic reports.
Aug 22: Head coach Matt LeFleur said Thursday that Morgan (shoulder) will be evaluated for the possibility of taking part in team drills, Ryan Wood of USA Today reports.
Aug 20: Dillard did not participate in Tuesday's practice session due to a shoulder injury, Matt Schneidman of The Athletic reports.
Aug 7: Kraft (pectoral) said Tuesday that he expects to be ready for the Packers' Week 1 game against Philadelphia, Ryan Wood of USA Today reports.
Jul 31: Valentine missed Wednesday's practice with a hamstring injury, Pete Dougherty of the Green Bay Press-Gazette reports.
Aug 20: Cooper (groin) was a limited participant in Tuesday's practice, Zach Jacobson of 247Sports.com reports.
